@startuml
title Attribute-Based Access Control (ABAC)

hide circle
hide empty members
skinparam backgroundColor transparent

class Subject {
  +subjectId: String
  +department: String
  +jobTitle: String
  +location: String
}

class Object {
  +objectId: String
  +type: String
  +ownerDepartment: String
  +sensitivity: String
}

class Action {
  +name: String
}

class Environment {
  +time: String
  +networkZone: String
}

class Policy {
  +evaluate(subject, object, action, environment): Boolean
}

Policy ..> Subject
Policy ..> Object
Policy ..> Action
Policy ..> Environment

note top of Policy
Decision is based on attributes of subject,
object, action, and environment.
Example:
department == ownerDepartment and time < 18:00
end note

@enduml